               <scopecontent id="aspace_fdb1dcbccb89952b6a6b482dd318ad90">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Reports prepared by hydraulic engineers from Colorado River Board, covering topics such as topography, drainage, climate, vegetation, water source and quality, history of development, agriculture, industry, business, and irrigation, among others. Included are numerous folded maps.</p>
               </scopecontent>
